#### Authorizations

HTTPBasicHTTPBearerHTTPBasicHTTPBearer

​

Authorization

string

header

required

Basic authentication header of the form `Basic <encoded-value>`, where `<encoded-value>` is the base64-encoded string `username:password`.

#### Path Parameters

​

entity

string

required

​

project

string

required

​

object_id

string

required

#### Query Parameters

​

digests

string[] | null

List of digests to delete. If not provided, all digests for the scorer will be deleted.

#### Response

Successful Response

​

num_deleted

integer

required

Number of scorer versions deleted

